snippet.title: EX APP Members Exposing the Reality of AAP

localized.description:
The IAC movement was started by Congress itself, much like how Independence movement was started by Britishers in the form of Congress. Later both went rogue.

Prominent ex AAP members Surajit Dasgupta & Rakesh Agrawal make some explosive claims about their party like

1. Some candidates were pre decided
2. Kejriwal crossed all levels of Divisive politics and at 1 instance went on to say "If we have to win elections, we have to ensure that 1 religion fights the other"
3. The AAM aadmi party became a 4 aadmi party, with Arvind only caring for Yogendra Yadav and Prashant Bhushan's family. Other members' views were blatantly ignored
4. How AAP used the network of Auto Drivers to do Publicity
5. How AAP Trolls are on payrolls of many NGOs wherein NGOs give salary to Trolls 

For many more such exposes, watch this full video.
